'''Every Best Singles +3''' is the first best of album of the [[j-pop|Japanese pop group]] [[Every Little Thing (band)|Every Little Thing]], released on March 31, 1999. It is the first album of songs from the best selling singles from the band with 2,556,314 copies sold, also becoming the 1st best selling album of all time in Japan.

